Package org.hibernate.query.spi

Class LongStreamDecorator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.query.spi.LongStreamDecorator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.util.stream.BaseStream<java.lang.Long,​java.util.stream.LongStream>, java.util.stream.LongStream
    public class LongStreamDecorator
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.stream.LongStream
    The LongStreamDecorator wraps a Java LongStream and registers a closeHandler which is passed further to any resulting Stream. The goal of the LongStreamDecorator is to close the underlying LongStream upon calling a terminal operation.
    Since:
    5.4
